The paper discusses the usage of semantic annotations to improve the online visibility of touristic service providers, which is closely related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and web technologies (cs.WEB). The paper also mentions the usage of intelligent applications, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The creation and deployment of semantic annotations involve structured data, which is related to databases (cs.DB). Finally, the paper mentions the understanding of content by search engines, which is related to natural language processing (cs.CL).
